                the inlet valve is broken, you'll need to replace it. Sometimes
                a quick reset of the machine can fix minor issues. Ensuring the
                water level switch is working correctly is also crucial. For
                more detailed information, refer to your washer's manual.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content__page-desc">
